{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_01UeeqPFGrjhpfSj2mmB7xXx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WCpYmK6KhgR3AuaEWS59Bx","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/root/bench/triso_sonnet/output/calculation_note.md","old_string":"| Case | Fluence x (10²⁵, E>0.18 MeV) | In-pile gas release fraction (end of irradiation) | Peak σ_p (MPa) | Peak σ_th (MPa) | σ_preload (MPa) | σ_net (MPa) | Pf (per particle) | **E[N failed]** | Onset (time, T) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| A1 | 3.55 | 0.935 | 107 | 21 | −6 | 122 | 1.4×10⁻⁷ | **0.002** | ~31 h into the 1600 °C hold (T≈1543 °C, still on the ramp) |\n| A2 | 5.45 | 0.280 | 148 | 41 | −26 | 164 | 1.5×10⁻⁶ | **0.024** | ~133 h, during the **1st 1800 °C hold** |\n| B  | 4.36 | 0.995 | 156 | 27 | −10 | 173 | 2.3×10⁻⁶ | **0.034** | ~155 h, during the **1st 1800 °C hold** (3rd stage) |\n| C1 | 6.82 | 0.853 | 191 | 23 | 0* | 213 | 1.2×10⁻⁵ | **0.020** | ~52 h into the 1600 °C hold (fast — most gas already released in-pile) |\n| C2 | 5.00 | 0.502 | 149 | 28 | −20 | 157 | 1.0×10⁻⁶ | **0.002** | ~158 h into the 1600 °C hold (slower — less gas pre-released in-pile) |","new_string":"Onset is defined as the first time, *within the final hold at the case's designated peak\ntemperature* (the \"case of interest\" per `02_cases.md` — this excludes locking onto a transient\nstress spike during an earlier intermediate excursion, e.g. A1's 1550 °C dwell before its\ndrop-and-reheat to 1600 °C), that the driving stress reaches 90% of its value at the end of that\nhold.\n\n| Case | Fluence x (10²⁵, E>0.18 MeV) | In-pile gas release fraction (end of irradiation) | Peak σ_p (MPa) | Peak σ_th (MPa) | σ_preload (MPa) | σ_net (MPa) | Pf (per particle) | **E[N failed]** | Onset (time, T) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| A1 | 3.55 | 0.935 | 107 | 21 | −6 | 122 | 1.4×10⁻⁷ | **0.002** | ~53.5 h — i.e. ~13 h into the final 1600 °C/500 h